Why Groundfloor?



Rates starting at 5.5%



Fix-and-flip hard money loans from $50,000 to $2,000,000 for
              residential properties (not owner-occupied)



Closing as fast as 15 days



No payments during term of loan



All points can be rolled into the loan



No personal guarantee required



Lend up to 70% ARV (after repair value)



Borrow up to 90% LTC (loan to cost)



Fast and simple application with minimal documentation (no tax returns, no bank statements)


A full list of our rates and fees can be found here.


Get A Rate Quote Now

          Get prequalified today and find out why NPR calls Groundfloor ‘Innovative” and why USA Today said developers have embraced Groundfloor.
          







