Boone's focus is creating and executing marketing programs that drive qualified leads that result in customers. He specializes in creating growth channels for startups, and believes in evidence-based, metrics-driven revenue growth through proven marketing methodologies. Boone has worked exclusively with Atlanta-based startups since moving to the area in 2014.
Boone hails from Auburn, Alabama. He received his BA from Birmingham-Southern College and MA from Savannah College of Art and Design.













